text: D is the fourth (number 4) letter in the alphabet. It comes from the Greek Delta and the Phoenician Dalet. == Meanings for D == * In education, D is one letter above a failing grade. * In electronics, D is a standard size dry cell battery. * In music, D is a note sometimes called “Re”. * In Roman numerals, D also means the number 500. * In computer programming, D is a programming language. ==Other websites==
